This code allows a Sparkfun device with gyroscope, accelerometer 
and compass to connect to an android device and read data.
It allows a user to control map by controlling the sensor. 
This code detects only FireFly bluetooth device (which then 
connects to Zephyr Sensor). For more specifications, email 
at any of the following address 

- Harshvardhan Vathsangam
    hvathsangam@gmail.com

- Ankit Sharma
    ankit@usc.edu